cs.DC, cs.PF, cs.MS, cs.NA, cs.SE 

This paper deals with load balancing in high-performance computing systems, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and performance analysis (cs.PF). The focus on scientific applications also suggests a possible connection to modeling and simulation (cs.MS) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Finally, the use of OpenMP and MPI libraries indicates a possible connection to software engineering (cs.SE).
